        <item>
            <title>华为余承东不再说「遥遥领先」，新金句：「强得飞起」+「靠抄袭没有未来」</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/27/huawei-yu-new-quote/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=huawei-yu-new-quote</link>
